Russia May Create Caucasus Silicon Valley, Kommersant Says

-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 
2011-08-25T05:06:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/russia-may-create-caucasus-silicon-valley-kommersant-says.html
Russia’s North Osetia-Alania
Republic proposed the creation of a so-called Caucasus Silicon
Valley to develop solar energy projects in the region,
 Kommersant  said, citing a statement from the area’s
administration.  The project would need investment of 32 billion rubles
($1.11 billion), Kommersant said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow 
